e","value":{"id":"構文","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> source <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> audioCtx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">createBufferSource</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nsource<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">stop</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>when<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>最も単純なオーディオバッファ再生の停止方法—この場合は何もパラメータを指定する必要はありません。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>source<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">stop</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>しばらく後に停止させたい場合は、引数として秒数を指定します。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>source<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">stop</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>Note:</strong> stop()の使い方の完全な例は<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BaseAudioContext/decodeAudioData\"><code>AudioContext.decodeAudioData</code></a>を参照してください。<a href=\"https://mdn.github.io/decode-audio-data/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">コードをすぐに実行する</a>ことや、<a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/decode-audio-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ソースコードを閲覧する</a>こともできます。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"引数","title":"引数","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"when\">when</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p><code>when</code>パラメータは、再生を<em>いつ</em>停止するかを決定します。指定の時間を経過すると、再生はすぐに停止します。このメソッドが 2 回以上呼ばれると、例外が発生します</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"戻り値","title":"戻り値","isH3":false,"content":"<p>なし</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"使用","title":"使用","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Specification</th>\n      <th>Status</th>\n      <th>Comment</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/webaudio/#widl-AudioBufferSourceNode-stop-void-double-when\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web Audio API<br><small lang=\"ja\">stop() の定義</small></a></td>\n      <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">勧告</span></td>\n      <td></td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザ互換性","id":"ブラウザ互換性","isH3":false,"query":"api.AudioScheduledSourceNode.stop","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/AudioScheduledSourceNode/stop/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参考","title":"参考","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Web_Audio_API/Using_Web_Audio_API\">Using the Web Audio API</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"構文"},{"text":"例","id":"例"},{"text":"引数","id":"引数"},{"text":"戻り値","id":"戻り値"},{"text":"使用","id":"使用"},{"text":"ブラウザ互換性","id":"ブラウザ互換性"},{"text":"参考","id":"参考"}],"summary":"インターフェースのstop()メソッドは、オーディオバッファの再生を停止させるために使われます。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"AudioScheduledSourceNode.stop()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"AudioScheduledSourceNode.stop()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/audioscheduledsourcenode/stop","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/audioscheduledsourcenode/stop/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374a